@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

autonumber

actor "HRM" as HRManager
participant ":System" as System

activate HRManager

HRManager -> System : Asks to assign skills to a specific employee
activate System

System --> HRManager :  Displays Employee ID list
deactivate System

HRManager -> System : Selects Employee ID number
activate System

System --> HRManager : Displays all Skills Already Assigned to that Employee and the Available Skills to Assign
deactivate System

HRManager -> System : Selects Skill Name(s) to assign and confirms
activate System

System -> System : Assigns Skill(s) to the Collaborator
System --> HRManager : Displays operation success message

deactivate System
@enduml
